Duke (the Java mascot)
================================================================================

The image scripts/gamebuilder/common/src/main/resources/duke_wave.png is the
Java mascot "Duke" in his classic waving pose, used as card art in the Game
Builder sample's "Duke Jack" tutorial. It was rasterized from the SVG
"File:Duke (Java mascot) waving.svg" on Wikimedia Commons and then trimmed and
downscaled; no changes were made to the artwork itself.

  Source: https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Duke_(Java_mascot)_waving.svg
